{
  "stem": "6526.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "To be able to go and to live in that, you had to have a place to-- of work.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we decided-- my brother and I decided we'll go into the small ghetto.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We'll pay somebody money to make believe that we working for them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But they couldn't take it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We didn't-- first of all, they, they couldn't take any more employees.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they did not have the place for us even to, to be there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So we decided not to.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "At that time, I with-- my brother and I decided that we should not be together.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "In case anything happened, it should not happen with both of us together, and I hide another place, not the place that I was originally with my friend, because I couldn't go back there alone.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But not far from him, there was a man that wanted to take me in.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So I was there for about a week to 10 days.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And every day, I heard him say, oh, the bread today is more money.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I don't know what it's going to be.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I have seen a guy-- one of these days-- either give me the money or get out.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So I went back to my brother and told him that I have decided to go in-- and that a ghetto is still a ghetto and people go in and out.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And they still make a living with this and that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I did not know that my cousins-- the rest of them-- the one that was killed-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] no, he was killed there the second time, not the first time.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Was killed-- that they were still there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when I came back to the ghetto the-- with my brother, we found the cousins there.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
